## Why This Is Asked

Tests practical use of private data paths, per-tenant isolation, and automated containment in a beginner-friendly scenario.

## Key Concepts

- VPC endpoints (S3 gateway, Interface/PrivateLink)
- Bucket policies with aws:SourceVpce and deny public access
- Per-tenant KMS CMKs and rotation
- Breach-containment via temporary STS revocation and IAM trust updates (60s)
- CloudTrail for verification

